CATEGORIES:ACADEMIC
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:404@bwa-calendar
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260424
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260425
SUMMARY:BWA: Week 2026 -  Professional Bike Health Checks
DESCRIPTION:Professional bike health checks available at school for Earth Week 2026. Advance booking required.\n\nAs part of Earth Week 2026 celebrations, the PTA is joining the APL to host a professional Bike Health Check service at the school. Pricing: 10 GBP for a small bike, 14 GBP for a big bike (24 inches and above). Booking: Advance booking is required at https://ecoledewixevents.bigcartel.com. Logistics: Drop off bikes between 8:00 AM and 9:00 AM in front of the school. Pick up at the end of the school day from inside the school grounds.
CATEGORIES:COMMUNITY
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:396@bwa-calendar
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260323
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260328
SUMMARY:BWA: No After School Boosters
DESCRIPTION:Reminder that there are no after school boosters this week.\n\nJust a reminder for those who have children attend after school boosters, there will be no boosters this week. Apologies for any inconvenience caused.
CATEGORIES:ADMIN
END:VEVENT
