UID:398@bwa-calendar
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260305
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260306
SUMMARY:BWA: World Book Day Dress Up
DESCRIPTION:Pupils are invited to dress as their favourite book character.\n\nTo celebrate World Book Day on Thursday 5th of March we are inviting pupils to dress as their favourite book character for the day. Please be imaginative and creative, but we strongly suggest children not bringing in props.
CATEGORIES:ARTS
END:VEVENT
