UID:405@bwa-calendar
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260423
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260424
SUMMARY:BWA: Deadline -  Notification of Student Departure for September
DESCRIPTION:Parents are requested to inform the school office in writing if their child will not be returning to BWA in September.\n\nThe school is planning for the next academic year. If your circumstances have changed and your child will not be returning to BWA in September, please inform the school office in writing as soon as possible, including details of the new school if known.
CATEGORIES:ADMIN
