BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:428@bwa-calendar
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260521
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260522
SUMMARY:BWA: PTA French & British Wine Tasting Evening
DESCRIPTION:Join the PTA for a French and British wine tasting evening at the school.\n\nJoin us for a French & British Wine Tasting Evening hosted by your PTA, a perfect chance to unwind, connect, and enjoy a touch of European charm. We’re excited to partner with Spy Wines, an independent London-based merchant. Expect a relaxed and sociable evening, great company, and plenty of wines to discover.
CATEGORIES:COMMUNITY
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:430@bwa-calendar
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260626
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260627
SUMMARY:BWA Y5b: Father's Day Celebration
DESCRIPTION:Father's Day celebration with tea, coffee, pastries, and classroom activities.\n\nIn celebration of the important role that fathers and father figures play in our lives, we have arranged a special event for Father's Day. We invite you to join us for tea, coffee and pastries in the canteen at 8:30am. At 9am, you will join your child in their classroom to enjoy a craft activity. The event will end around 9:30am.
CATEGORIES:COMMUNITY
END:VEVENT
