SUMMARY:BWA: International Families Day Buffet
DESCRIPTION:International Families Day buffet event.\n\nThank you for your continued support for our upcoming International Families Day. Please come to the front office from 2:30pm to be shown to the hall and complete a slip with your dish details. We really appreciate your support and look forward to enjoying the variety of food together.
CATEGORIES:COMMUNITY
